title: Prison Architect alpha 22 cracked (3dmgames)
description:
The other Prison Architect alpha 22 torrent on TPB has hidden demo-limitations: A time-limit that could be bypassed, and a max prisoner limit (around 50-70) that couldn't. 


I'm no way responsible for the crack, just found it on another site. Tested, and it works.


INSTALL:

You can just extract the files and play, it works if you overwrite your previous PA installation. Make sure to tell your antivirus to skip scanning "steam_api.dll" as it gives the usual false positive.


The archive has some URL files in it too. I wouldn't even poke them with a stick. Be warned!
